name: eLibrary
tagline: eLibrary is a JavaScript library for highlighting HTML elements.
body:
eLibrary is pure FP, provides both OOP-style and procedural-style API which offers some util tools for HTML elements highlighting.
For more information, see README(https://github.com/bombless/eLibrary/blob/master/README.md).
